.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to support the student in acquiring knowledge and skills that
support 1) consciously and expediently the planning and completion of studies in the chosen curriculum, and 2) planning of career goals.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Student who has passed the course: 1) consciously and expediently plans his or her studies in the curriculum Teaching Humanities and Social Subjects in Basic School 2) is aware of his or her own peculiarities as a learner and is able to take them into account when studying; 3) knows the possibilities of working and continuing education in the field of education, and based on them is able to plan his or her studies and set career goals; 4) has regularly analyzed his / her experience as a learner during his / her studies (including the strengths and weaknesses related to future career), 5) is able to make sense of his / her studies and relate them to own development.
